docs.abstract: Britain and the European Union now face the all-but-impossible task of drawing up a comprehensive trade deal in a year’s time.
docs.snippet: Britain and the European Union now face the all-but-impossible task of drawing up a comprehensive trade deal in a year’s time.
docs.lead_paragraph: LONDON — Like ex-spouses who have just signed divorce papers but not yet begun the ugly business of dividing their possessions, Britain and the European Union are tiptoeing around each other as the year begins, desperate to keep their dealings civil even as they gird for the unpleasantness to come.

headline.main: And You Thought Brexit Was Tough …
headline.print_headline: Britain and E.U. Smile, But Expect Gritted Teeth

docs.abstract: Igor Shesterkin of the Rangers got his chance as Henrik Lundqvist, the longtime goalie and perennial fan favorite, watched from the bench.
docs.snippet: Igor Shesterkin of the Rangers got his chance as Henrik Lundqvist, the longtime goalie and perennial fan favorite, watched from the bench.
docs.lead_paragraph: His every move has been chronicled and touted on social media. And on Tuesday, the night finally came for 24-year-old Igor Shesterkin to make his much anticipated debut in goal for the Rangers. Henrik Lundqvist, 37, who has more wins than any other goalie as a Ranger, was on the bench, possibly a first step toward a changing of the guard.

headline.main: A Great Goaltending Hope Arrives With a Win
headline.print_headline: A Potential Heir of ‘King Henrik’ Holds Court at the Garden

docs.abstract: The designer Rodolphe Parente is a master of mixing unexpected textures and eras, as his latest project proves.
docs.snippet: The designer Rodolphe Parente is a master of mixing unexpected textures and eras, as his latest project proves.
docs.lead_paragraph: The Paris-based architect and designer Rodolphe Parente refuses to subscribe to a signature style. “On each project, we create a different story; we try to have the right tone, to develop the right emotion,” the 39-year-old says of his narrative-driven approach, which is based on interpreting a client’s desires instead of imposing his own mark. For one recent apartment redesign in Monte Carlo, the unique Mediterranean light and the Modernist building itself inspired Parente to work with textured materials that would be enhanced by the changing shadows; by contrast, in 2015 he transformed a Parisian apartment built in 1910 into a spare futuristic pod with concrete walls and glossy red floors, channeling the client’s devotion to Buddhism, modern architecture and David Lynch.

headline.main: In Paris, an Apartment Where Picassos Meet 17th-Century Antiques
headline.print_headline: By Design; Every Room Tells a Story

docs.abstract: The leafy Bergen County township is seeing an influx of young families, who value its small-town atmosphere and relatively low taxes.

docs.lead_paragraph: Daniela Panetta is from Westchester County and her fiancé, Rob Cappadora, is from Long Island, but when they decided to buy a home they chose Wyckoff, a leafy township in northwest Bergen County, N.J., that they discovered after visiting a friend nearby.

headline.main: Wyckoff, N.J.: A Peaceful Suburb With a Sense of Community

docs.abstract: Angry and disaffected, the “Prozac Nation” author, who died this week at 52, found new peace and purpose in her later years.
docs.snippet: Angry and disaffected, the “Prozac Nation” author, who died this week at 52, found new peace and purpose in her later years.
docs.lead_paragraph: With Kurt Cobain, Tupac Shakur, Elliott Smith and Jeff Buckley gone, that undersized, underwhelming demographic known as Generation X was already short on idols. And after the death this past Tuesday of Elizabeth Wurtzel, the “Prozac Nation” author and 1990s-angst poster child, our confused, self-contradictory cohort may have lost the most Gen X member of us all.

headline.main: Elizabeth Wurtzel Finally Grew Up, Like the Rest of Gen X
